OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAfternoon
OL,6,Fsunny spells persisting through the
OL,7,Fevening with clear spells developing
OL,8,Fovernight. This will allow for a
OL,9,Frather chilly night in places and a
OL,10,Frural frost to develop in prone spots.
OL,11,FLight winds throughout.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FEarly sunshine will give way
OL,14,Fto an increase in cloud from the east
OL,15,Fon Monday. Perhaps a few showers
OL,16,Fdeveloping through the afternoon.
OL,17,FGentle easterly breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
