OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FTuesday will start rather cloudy with
OL,7,Fisolated showers, brightening up
OL,8,Flater. Dry with sunny spells on
OL,9,FWednesday and Thursday, though a brisk
OL,10,Fwind developing, making it feel cool
OL,11,Fat times.
